Package: game-req-analyzer
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.28), libstdc++6 (>= 9), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.0)
Maintainer: GameReqAnalyzer Team <team@gamereqanalyzer.com>
Description: Premium Game System Requirements Analyzer
 GameReqAnalyzer is a powerful tool for analyzing game directories and
 generating detailed system requirements recommendations. It scans game
 files, analyzes assets (textures, models, audio, scripts, executables),
 and provides minimum and recommended hardware specifications based on
 the actual requirements of the game.
 .
 Features:
   - Comprehensive analysis of textures, 3D models, audio files, scripts, and executables
   - Accurate requirements calculation based on actual asset analysis
   - Up-to-date hardware database with CPU, GPU, RAM, and storage benchmark data
   - Interactive terminal UI with colorized output and progress indicators
   - Multiple output formats: terminal, JSON, CSV, HTML, and Markdown
   - Cross-platform support for Windows, macOS, and Linux
   - Extensible design for adding new file format analyzers
Homepage: https://github.com/yourusername/GameReqAnalyzer
